00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:35.480
Such sculptures that we had on us were probably one of the biggest.

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:36.760
The costies, yeah.

00:07:36.760 --> 00:07:37.560
In the carnival.

00:07:37.560 --> 00:07:41.640
And there was a lot of attention on us, especially when we got to the end

00:07:41.640 --> 00:07:43.720
and we were just out in the castle.

00:07:44.200 --> 00:07:47.080
So many people wanted photos and that was really odd.

00:07:47.880 --> 00:07:49.560
Ren basically had a shamanic experience.

00:07:51.560 --> 00:07:53.800
She went into dragon mode and she wasn't Ren anymore.

00:07:55.800 --> 00:07:57.560
Jumping around like, I was a fly.

