I was in an altar state, definitely.

00:08:06.280 --> 00:08:06.760
Really?

00:08:06.760 --> 00:08:07.320
It's good.

00:08:07.320 --> 00:08:08.280
That's funny.

00:08:08.280 --> 00:08:09.240
That's fantastic.

00:08:09.240 --> 00:08:10.840
She was photobombing my photos.

00:08:10.840 --> 00:08:11.480
Yeah, I was like.

00:08:11.960 --> 00:08:18.680
Yeah, the thing about that particular parade is that you get to see in such sort of explicit

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:24.360
and again, celebratory party manner, all the different sort of communities, basically.

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:28.840
So you have people and they're all, you know, the Malaysians of Cardiff or so and so.

00:08:28.840 --> 00:08:32.280
It's just so great that everybody's coming together into that thing.

00:08:32.280 --> 00:08:33.240
It just doesn't happen.

00:08:34.760 --> 00:08:37.480
And it makes you realise how many different communities there are in Cardiff.

00:08:37.480 --> 00:08:39.160
Yeah, hidden communities for most of us.

00:08:39.880 --> 00:08:41.000
Yes, definitely.

00:08:41.560 --> 00:08:44.120
And you're both practicing artists.

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:47.480
I want to again, just for austerity, for we are talking into the future here.

00:08:48.360 --> 00:08:50.680
Would you care to say a little bit about yourself as an artist?

00:08:50.680 --> 00:08:54.680
You're yeah, well, you've come and practice a statement from Ren.

00:08:55.400 --> 00:08:56.200
What do you think, Ren?

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:59.000
