00:09:02.600 --> 00:09:03.560
It's quite explicit.

00:09:03.560 --> 00:09:04.680
It's about the body.

00:09:04.680 --> 00:09:07.720
It's about boundaries and a lot of it's about sex.

00:09:07.720 --> 00:09:13.800
So I try to sort of broach to be subjects by basically throwing it in people's face.

00:09:13.800 --> 00:09:14.440
And it's comic.

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:18.600
Yeah.

