00:09:24.600 --> 00:09:31.160
I'm also trying to set up an open mic for specifically to

00:09:31.960 --> 00:09:36.600
try to encourage people to perform, like to experiment performance as well.

00:09:36.600 --> 00:09:37.720
And it's called Duke.

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:38.600
You're not trying to set it up.

00:09:38.600 --> 00:09:39.160
You are setting it up.

00:09:39.160 --> 00:09:39.640
Yeah, I am.

00:09:41.160 --> 00:09:41.320
Yeah.

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:41.960
And also I'm...

00:09:41.960 --> 00:09:42.840
Listen to your manager.

00:09:43.960 --> 00:09:49.720
I'm also in the third year of uni and my dissertation is creative writing

00:09:49.720 --> 00:09:52.040
and is also focused on female sexuality.

00:09:52.040 --> 00:09:56.920
So it felt very much synchronous for me to...

00:09:56.920 --> 00:09:58.760
To go through that experience in carnival.

00:09:58.760 --> 00:09:59.240
Yeah.

00:09:59.240 --> 00:10:01.240
